snippet.title: Best VGM 902 - Castlevania : Dawn of Sorrow - After the Battle ~Blue Recollection~
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 224 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mea-D-VFzck
Best VGM 511 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mG9BcQEApoI
Best VGM 813 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4fMd_2XeXLA
Best VGM 1396 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T586T6QFjqE
Best VGM 2371 - https://youtu.be/lBI7g1oOud8

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Castlevania: Dawn of Sorrow (2005)
After the Battle ~Blue Recollection~
Eriko Imura
